ftd companies  corporate responsibility     corporate responsibility careers job opportunities benefits life at ftd companies corporate responsibility ftd corporate giving strategy we understand how important it is to give back to those in need as a good corporate citizen and now as a newly integrated company we can do even more to help make a difference in others lives to that end we are very pleased to announce ftds newly redesigned corporate giving strategy as we examined our approach to giving back we wanted to ensure that our charitable efforts align to our mission vision and values as well as to our overall business objectives we also wanted to find ways to engage you as employees through new programs and charities where we can make the biggest impact we created an overarching pillar for ftd community support our corporate giving strategy will strive to create inspiring and meaningful moments that positively impact the communities in which we live and do business in to carry out this mission we are establishing longterm charitable partnerships for each of the brands with this overarching pillar in mind ftd companies  about ftd companies     about ftd companies company info about ftd companies about ftd about interflora about proflowers about additional brands management history privacy policy terms  conditions ftd companies inc is a premier floral and gifting company through our diversified family of brands we provide floral specialty foods gifts and related products to consumers primarily in the united states and the united kingdom we also provide floral products and services to retail florists and other retail locations throughout these same geographies ftd has been delivering flowers since  and the highlyrecognized ftd® and interflora® brands are supported by the iconic mercury man logo® which is displayed in nearly  floral shops in over  countries in addition to ftd and interflora our diversified portfolio of brands includes the following trademarks proflo